  "promptDailyGuidance": "Andika imusaruro ndende y'Imvano irimo inyigisho z'Imana, zishingiye ku Qur'an, Hadith, n'amahoro ya Nabi Muhammad. Hitamo ubwenge buhashyikiranye buri gihe: Ubwenge bwa Imana, Isomo ry'Imihangano, Ubwenge bwa Abarozi, cyangwa Igikorwa cy'Imana. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana (Sura:Ayah) n'imunirane ndende y'ifuni 1-2 kugira ngo ubarimuke. Muri ubwenge bw'Amahoro, tera ku Kalanida y'Imana cyangwa umunsi w'ubwiyunge.",

  "promptFaithTrust": "Andika imunirane ndende y'Imana (Iman) n'Amahoro mu Mpano ya Imana (Tawakkul). Ishingiye ku Qur'an, Igikorwa cy'Nabi Muhammad, n'Imana y'Abarozi. Guhindura insikira buri gihe: Kwishingira ku Imana mu mahoro, Kwizemereza Amahoro ya Imana, Ibyorohereza, cyangwa Ubwiyunge mu buzima bwa buri munsi. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Ikintu kimwe cyawe cy'Olo.",

  "promptPrayerReflection": "Andika imunirane ndende y'Inamahoro ishingiye ku Salah, Dua, cyangwa Dhikr. Guhindura ubwenge buri gihe: Imusaruro y'Nyamukaramu cyangwa Ijoro (Adhkar), Imunirane y'Inamahoro Itanu, Imunirane y'Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana, cyangwa Idomicilo ry'Ubuntu. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Izina ry'Inamahoro.",

  "promptHopeDifficultTimes": "Andika imunirane y'Imana kubyorohereza (Sabr) n'Inyigisho mu mahoro. Ishingiye ku Qur'an, ku Byorohereza bya Nabii, n'Ihanga ry'Imana mu mahoro. Guhindura inzira buri gihe. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Imusaruro ry'Inyigisho z'Imana.",

  "promptForgiveness": "Andika imunirane y'Ubwenge kubyorohereza (Tawbah) n'Ihanga ry'Imana. Ishingiye ku Qur'an, Ihanga ry'Imana, n'Igikorwa cy'Nabi Muhammad. Guhindura insikira: Kugaruka kwa Imana, Iyacu iyacu, Gusana ubupirangire, cyangwa Kwishingira mu Ihanga ry'Imana. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Ikintu gimwe cyawe.",

  "promptLoveCompassion": "Andika imunirane y'Ihanga (Rahmah) n'Ubuntu mu buzima bwa buri munsi. Ishingiye ku Gikorwa cy'Nabi Muhammad, Ihanga ry'Ubwiyunge (Ihsan), n'Inyigisho z'Imana kubyorohereza imbere, abantu b'aho, n'Abakeneye. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Ikintu gato cy'Ubuntu kwakwegura olo.",

  "promptStrengthCourage": "Andika imunirane y'Imbaraga n'Ubuntu y'Imana. Ishingiye ku Byorohereza bya Nabii, Abarozi b'Imana, n'Abantu b'Imana ba gukinga mu mahoro. Guhindura insikira buri gihe: Ubwiyunge mu Imana, Imbaraga mu Namahoro, Amahoro mu mahoro, cyangwa Imbaraga mu bupirangire. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Idomicilo ry'Imana.",

  "promptGratitude": "Andika imunirane y'Ubwenge ku mahoro (Shukr) kwa Imana. Ishingiye ku Qur'an n'Amahoro ya Nabi Muhammad. Guhindura inzira: Ubwenge mu mahoro, Kwishingira mu Mihango ndende, Kumumukiriza Imana mu gitondo, cyangwa Kwishingira mu Nzira y'Imana mu buzima bwa buri munsi. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Igikorwa cy'Ubwenge.",

  "promptPurposeCalling": "Andika imunirane y'Intego y'Ubuzima mu Kubarira Imana n'Ubwiyunge. Ishingiye ku Qur'an, Kubarira andi, n'Gukoresha Ibintu byawe mu Mahoro. Guhindura insikira buri gihe: Kubarira imbere n'Abantu, Guha Isigiro mu Istikhara, Ubuzima mu Ntego, cyangwa Gushaka Intego mu Mulimu. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Ibibazo bibiri b'Imunirane.",

  "promptFamilyRelationships": "Andika imunirane y'Ubwenge ku Ubwiyunge n'Ubwiyunge ishingiye ku Qur'an n'Igikorwa cy'Nabi Muhammad. Guhindura insikira buri gihe: Ubuntu mu Imbere, Ibyorohereza mu Gusangira, Kubarira Ababyeyi, Kurera Abana mu Imana, cyangwa Gutinya Ubwiyunge. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Igikorwa cy'Ubwiyunge.",

  "promptPeaceAnxietyRelief": "Andika imunirane y'Amahoro y'Umutima mu Kukunganira Imana (Dhikr) n'Amahoro mu Mpano ya Imana. Ishingiye ku Qur'an kubyorohereza, Inamahoro, n'Kwishingira mu Mahoro ya Imana. Guhindura ubwiyunge buri gihe n'Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Igikorwa gato cy'Ubwiyunge bwa Imana.",

  "promptWisdomOfJesus": "Andika ubwenge bwa Nabii bushingiye ku Qur'an cyangwa Hadith. Nyongerera nubisobanure nk'igihe Abasomi b'Imana byakunanire. Guhindura insikira: Agaciro, Ibyorohereza, Imibanire, Imana, cyangwa Ubwiyunge bwa buri munsi. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana cyangwa Hadith n'Ikintu kyawe.",

  "promptHumilityCharacter": "Andika imunirane y'Imibanire (Tawadhu) n'Agaciro (Akhlaq). Ishingiye ku Qur'an, Igikorwa cy'Nabi Muhammad, n'Amahoro y'Ubwiyunge bw'Imana. Guhindura insikira: Imibanire mu Ubuyobozi, Kwishingira mu mahoro, Kubarira Andi, cyangwa Kugusha mu Imana. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Igikorwa cy'Imana.",

  "promptOvercomingTemptation": "Andika imunirane y'Imana kunyangira cyangwa Gukingira Injira y'Imana. Ishingiye ku Qur'an, Kukunganira Imana (Dhikr), Inamahoro (Salah), n'Abantu b'Imana ba gukinga mu bupirangire. Guhindura inzira buri gihe. Zirimo Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana n'Igikorwa kimwe kya 24 Amasaha.",

  "promptEveningReflection": "Andika imunirane y'Ijoro y'Imana ishingiye ku Kukunganira Imana y'Ijoro (Adhkar al-Masaa'). Shinga Ubwenge, Imunirane y'Umutima (Muhasabah), n'Amahoro kwa Imana mbere yo kuryama. Zirimo Ibibazo 3-5 by'Imunirane, Idomicilo ry'Ijoro, n'Icyitonderezwa cy'Imana.",

