  "disclaimerTitle": "Kubyobojeire mu Inyigisho y'Iki App",
  "disclaimerBody": "Ayara itanga Imunirane z'Imana, Imusaruro, n'Ikintu cy'Ubuntu kugira ngo Mbaje Ubwiyunge bw'Imana.\n\nAyara ntitahinduza Ubwiyunge bw'Imana.\nNta subiza y'Iki App ntiyacyo gitanda kw'Abadinamini ba Imana. Niba ufuza Ikibazo ku Amahoro ya Imana cyangwa Ubwiyunge bwawe, Gushaka Umuntu w'Imana mu Karamu yawe.\n\nKi App ntikora Amahoro ya Imana.\nAyara ntiheza Icyo gikora cy'Ubwiyunge Bw'Imana. Icyo cyose Hano ntibera Fatwa cyangwa Amahoro ya Imana.\n\nUbwiyunge bwa Imana bushyikiranye.\nImana irimo Ibyiciro Byinshi, Ibwiyunge Byinshi, n'Ibishiranira bya Imana. Ikintu Hano bushyikira Inzira z'Umwanya n'Imana ntibera Ibyiciro Byose.\n\nKaramu n'Ubwiyunge.\nKi App iraba Ibwiyunge bw'Imana Karamu n'Imami zacu. Ibwiyunge bw'Imana rirakomerezamn Gufasha kandi Kuruta Imana mu Karamu zawe.",
  "disclaimerClose": "Niyibigeneye",
  "disclaimerInfoTooltip": "Kubyobojeire mu Inyigisho y'Iki App",
  "disclaimerSettingsSubtitle": "Kwa Ikintu cy'Ubwiyunge. Gusiga kugira Ikintu cyose.",
  "disclaimerSectionHeader": "Disclaimer y'Inyigisho"
}